弗莱彻 (FLETCHER) 分享新单曲《Lead Me On》，宣布新专辑https://www.nme.com/news/music/fletcher-new-single-lead-me-on-announces-album-in-search-of-the-antidote-3579028?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=fletcher-新单曲引导我宣布专辑寻找解药Eli OrdonezTue, 30 Jan 2024 06:22:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3579028 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《寻找解药》三月上映</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fletcher-new-single-lead-me-on-announces-album-in-search-of-the-antidote-3579028">弗莱彻 (FLETCHER) 分享了新单曲“Lead Me On”的消息，并宣布新专辑</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/fletcher@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fletcher">弗莱彻 (FLETCHER)</a>宣布推出她的大二全长专辑《In Search Of The Antidote》，并发行了主打单曲《Lead Me On》。</p><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fletcher-nme-affirmations-girl-of-my-dreams-3457242"><b>弗莱彻：“在我上台之前，我告诉自己：‘你就是那个婊子’”</b></a></li></ul><p>这位新泽西歌手的失恋歌曲于上周晚些时候发布，标志着她与 2022 年首张专辑《Girl Of My Dreams》中精致、梦幻的音景不同，转而偏向流行摇滚。 《Lead Me On》中弗莱彻反思了一段单相思，其诗句详细描述了她和情人之间的差异（“<em>我生来就是为了找到你/但你的心一直在奔跑/只是从来没有走向我</em>”），最后以一个宣泄的钩子：“<em>那你为什么不引导我/因为有总比什么都没有好</em>”。</p><p>这首歌曲还附有亚历山大·摩尔斯 (Alexandre Moors) 执导的一段视频，视频中描绘了这位歌手在一栋波西米亚人居住的大房子的房间里漫步的情景。观看下面的“引导我”视频： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="FLETCHER - 带领我前进（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4paMNQf1b2o?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Lead Me On》是 FLETCHER 即将推出的第二张全长专辑《In Search Of The Antidote》的主打单曲，该专辑将于 3 月 22 日通过 Capitol/EMI Records 发行 - 请<a href="https://shop.findingfletcher.com/?utm_source=Original&amp;utm_campaign=20240123&amp;utm_medium=channel.utm_medium&amp;utm_referrer=https%3A%2F%2Ffletcher.lnk.to%2FAntidotePR&amp;utm_board=capitol-records-us&amp;utm_country=US&amp;utm_linkurl=fletcher.lnk.to%2FAntidoteStore&amp;lf=2905bd0618392b8bf38960726dc0a8cc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。</p><p>詹妮弗·德西尔维奥 (Jennifer Decilveo) 曾为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/take-that">Take That</a> 、麦莉·赛勒斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">Miley Cyrus)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hozier">霍齐尔 (Hozier)</a>等乐队创作过歌曲，并与乔恩·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jon-bellion">贝利昂 (Jon Bellion</a> )、朱莉娅·迈克尔斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julia-michaels">Julia Michaels</a> )、迈克尔·波拉克 (Michael Pollack) 等人共同创作歌曲，制作了这张唱片。</p><p>这位歌手在一份新闻稿中表示，这张专辑将为歌迷提供对“身份、不安全感、自我和自我实现”主题的内省，并得出“爱是解药”的结论。 “多年来，我在很多事情上寻找解药：女人、道路、舞台、粉丝、灵性和自我反思，”她写道。 “制作这张专辑是一次挖掘，一次深入的探索，我问自己什么才能真正治愈我，而我最终的认识是，爱是解药。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2fZqiPxHEr/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.