ews/film/ayo-edebiri-drops-out-of-marvels-thunderbolts-3579008">阿约·艾德比里 (Ayo Edebiri) 退出漫威《雷电》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
